captions.text:
This game is called "Narrators".
Everybody plays.

We'll improvise a scene,
always with one narrator

and the others play the scene.
When I ring the bell, we change narrators.

Right? I'll need a book.
Anyone in the audience has a book?
Here's a book.

I've never returned a book to the
library and I won't start now.
Here... 'Thy Neighbor's Wife'.

I'll pick up a sentence...
I'll pick a random part of this book,
and that's going to be our theme.

'Barbara found the plain country women
collectively unattractive.'

So, once again,
the game is "Narrators"

and 'Barbara found the plain country
girls unattractive', beginning now!

This is Barbara.
A girl born and raised in the country.
She had strict parents.
They didn't like when she...

When she... Stared at
those boys riding bikes.
Newspaper!
Barbara, this is for city people.
And city people shouldn't behave like you...
You shouldn't behave like city people!
Oh, that's much better, daddy!
She wanted to become a floozy city woman!
I want to go to college!
College, girl?
You'll milk cows!

- But daddy...
- Barbara went to milk the cow...
Daddy!

And while milking the cow,
Barbara had a vision!
This cow only has one tit!
Barbara!

Barbara, I'll visit the neighbor's farm...
Don't mess around, okay?

- See ya! - And Barbara,
with a wild look in her eyes...

Imagined that in the city there would be
other kinds of one-titted cows.
Then she left secretly to the big city!
Hey, motherfucker!
Wow!
She was amazed with everything!
Move over, bitch!

- That's when a car...
- You skank!
That's when a car accidentally hit her!

The man quickly got out of
the car and carried Barbara...
She was still in slow motion!

- My dear!
- He brought her to the hospital!
I can still walk!
There, the doctor looked into his eyes...
And said:
You have a rare specimen in front of you.
She's a country woman!

I barely know her...
But...

Yes...
Exactly!
She still has her hymen!
Damn!
So he took her home...

Where he introduced her
to his wife, Rejane.
Rejane, this woman has her hymen!
That's a hard thing to find nowadays!

CIA. BARBIXAS DE HUMOR
presented

IMPROVÁVEL
Probably a good show.

dizer que está diretamente ligado à virgindade feminina. Didaticamente, 
gostaria que você imaginasse um túnel. E no meio desse túnel, há um

quiser atravessar esse túnel, esse plástico acaba se rompendo pra sempre. O 
plástico é o hímem, já o túnel e o trem vou deixar para que você faça a 
associação, certo? O hímem impede a passagem de bactérias e é necessário 
somente enquanto a menina ainda é jovem pois quando ela fica mais velha, 
seu corpo já tem todas as formas de se proteger. A biologia é maravilhosa,
